title: Get Ready For The Long-Haul With The Gemini Travel Pack
description: It's clean on the outside and organized on the inside. A 270 degree zipper gives easy access to multiple pockets and sleeves on the move; open the zipper all the way for super efficient packing and unpacking. The Gemini pack allows you to travel in style
